function_call.name: get_risks
function_call.arguments: {"risks":[{"Description":"The assessment contains questions about anxiety symptoms and severity, insomnia severity, and impulsivity levels, which may indicate mental health risks.","Impact":"Without proper mitigation, individuals at risk of mental health issues may experience worsening symptoms and an overall decline in well-being.","Mitigation":"Proper mental health support, counseling, and interventions can help mitigate the impact of mental health risks.","Technologies":"Mental health apps, telemedicine platforms, and online counseling services can be used to provide support and interventions.","People":"Individuals responding to the assessment, especially those with existing mental health concerns or vulnerabilities.","Owner":"Mental health professionals, counselors, and healthcare providers can implement the mitigation efforts."}]}
